data.description: Discover the charm of this adorable 3 bed, 2 bath single -story home in the sought-after Napa Hills Community in Summerlin. Featuring a gated front for added privacy, en-suite master, and a spacious backyard with a patio and palm trees. The soft water system and alkaline water is already paid for. The house comes Solar-equipped with a hassle free assumable loan from the solar company. Minutes away from Downtown Summerlin and Red Rock Casino. Walking distance to Arbors Tennis and Play Park, The Summerlin CSN,Sig Rogich, Palo Verde HS and Pavilion Center pool.
